# NSE Options Chain Trading Platform

A professional NSE-compliant options chain trading platform with beginner and professional trading modes, basket functionality, and responsive design.

## Features
- Real-time options chain simulation
- Symbol and expiry selection
- Trading mode toggle (Beginner/Professional)
- Basket for multi-leg strategies
- Trade execution flow (demo)
- Search and filtering
- Responsive layout for desktop and mobile

## Usage
1. Clone the repository:
   ```
   git clone https://github.com/CHIBOLAR/Options-chain-prototype.git
   ```
2. Push your local files to the repo:
   ```
   git add .
   git commit -m "Initial commit"
   git push origin main
   ```
3. Enable GitHub Pages in repository settings (set source to root or `/docs`).

## Live Demo
Once GitHub Pages is enabled, visit:  
`https://chibolar.github.io/Options-chain-prototype/`

